data.description: Come take a look at this charming 4 bedroom 2 bath, 1614 sq. ft home! Located in the desirable SW Visalia area, this home has many updated features! Newer 3 year old life-time roof, additional insulation added in the attic, and energy efficient dual pane windows help to maximize efficiency. As you walk though the front door you will see a large open living room with lots of natural light, brick fireplace, and lots of room to hang out with family and friends. The cheerful kitchen features tile counter top, pretty accent backsplash, stainless steel five burner cook top, and dishwasher.  Brand new carpet was just installed last winter in all bedrooms. The hall bath and master bath have been updated with custom tile. The master bath features a large corner shower, and cute cabinet/sink with vintange charm! Step out into the back yard to a large patio perfect for entertaining and creating memories. This lovely home has been home to a family for many years, now its ready for a new family!
